headline: CNO Q4 Earnings Beat on Higher Annuity & Health Premiums
summary: CNO Financial's Q4 results reflect improved collected premiums in its three product lines, partly offset by a decline in net investment income. It estimates 2025 operating EPS to stay within the band of $3.70-$3.90.
